sentences.english: Young women’s employment has stagnated and is well below that of young men.
sentences.chinese: 女青年的就業率停滯了，而且大大低於男青年。

sentences.english: GDP has lurched sickeningly downward, but employment has not.
sentences.chinese: 國內生產總值急劇下滑，但就業率還算大致穩定。

sentences.english: THW allocate college enrollment quota based on each insititution's graduate employment rate.
sentences.chinese: 大學的入學名額應基於畢業生的就業率來分配。

sentences.english: THIS percentage of secondary vocational school grads found jobs last year.
sentences.chinese: 這是去年職業中學的就業率。

sentences.english: Every group with lower education levels saw employment numbers decline.
sentences.chinese: 每個年齡羣中教育程度較低的人就業率下降。

sentences.english: Payrolls were below year-earlier levels in 48 of the 50 states.
sentences.chinese: 50個州中的48個州就業率低於年初水平。

sentences.english: They create two out of every three new jobs in this country.
sentences.chinese: 它們創造了這個國家三分之二的就業率。
